      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 You have to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s been treated like royalty and is in truly flawless condition\u2014it honestly still has that wonderful new car smell. Not a single scratch or dent to be found; it's basically been living in a bubble! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. If you want a ride that feels and looks brand new without the dealership headache, this is your lucky day! Drop me a message, I'd love to chat!",
