      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its factory-fresh appearance inside and out. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks or stone chips, while the interior remains in showroom condition\u2014the leather is supple, the carpets are spotless, and it still carries that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting every fluid change and inspection. Every button, switch, and feature operates with the precision of the day it left the assembly line. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
